美欧亚股市全线下跌，疫情开始影响全球经济走向。
The U. S. -Eurasian stock market fell across the board, and the epidemic began to affect the global economy.
金焱。
Yan, Jin.
财经杂志                      。
Financial magazine.
财经杂志。
